name: Moon Records (5)
profile:
Label history :
1982 - "[l=Alfa Moon, Inc.]" was founded by Ryouzou Kosugi. "Moon Records" was started as [l=Alfa Moon]'s label.
1990 - Alfa Moon was acquired by [l=Warner Music Group]. Company name was changed to "[l=MMG Inc.]".
1993 - Company name was changed to [l=EastWest Japan].
2002 - [l=Warner Music Japan Inc.], EastWest Japan, Time Warner Entertainment Japan was merged. New company name was "Warner Entertainment Japan".
2004 - [l=Warner Music Group] was acquired by WMG Acquisition Corp(Delaware US.).
